12362
07:50:03,180 --> 07:50:06,119
To keep you safe as long as I can.

12363
07:50:06,180 --> 07:50:10,080
In this book, are my visions of what is

12364
07:50:10,080 --> 07:50:10,680
yet to come.

12365
