12396
07:51:28,860 --> 07:51:30,959
If you remember a few things.

12397
07:51:31,020 --> 07:51:33,779
We are here to love with our whole

12398
07:51:33,779 --> 07:51:34,319
hearts.

12399
07:51:34,380 --> 07:51:37,799
Lean into your kindness and empathy in

12400
07:51:37,799 --> 07:51:40,860
the face of evil, but do not let evil

12401
07:51:40,860 --> 07:51:41,040
win.

12402
07:51:41,099 --> 07:51:43,979
You are the only dragon who can decide

12403
07:51:43,979 --> 07:51:44,939
who you want to be.

12404
07:51:45,000 --> 07:51:47,939
Don't let yourself get stuck on someone

12405
07:51:47,939 --> 07:51:48,900
else's path.

12406
07:51:48,959 --> 07:51:52,439
Search for what's true, and think for

12407
07:51:52,439 --> 07:51:52,740
yourself.

12408
07:51:52,799 --> 07:51:55,439
Over a 100 years ago.

12409
07:51:55,500 --> 07:51:58,560
I thought my life was finished, and there

12410
07:51:58,560 --> 07:52:00,119
